      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i walk through the house and it feels like i'm just a ghost wandering around. there's no point to any of it, honestly. i wake up, i eat, i sleep... but the person i was supposed to be with isn't here. i feel like half of me just died with them and what's left is just... empty.",
